---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
import { site } from "../data/siteContent";
---

<Section bg="bg-surface" padding="py-12 lg:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-accent text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-3">
      Limited Availability
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text">
      LIMITED WEEKLY DEPLOYMENT CAPACITY
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      We run a controlled number of projects per week to maintain the quality standards our clients expect.
      We do not stack jobs, rush timelines, or cut corners to squeeze in extra work.
      If your project requires scheduling beyond our current availability, we will tell you upfront.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="/quote" class="btn btn-primary">
        Check Availability &amp; Request Scoping
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
